nodes.text: Aurebesh soup was a soup dish served at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant under the Pantoran Plate Specials section on the menu. Aurebesh soup was a flavorful topato soup with pasta shapes in the form of Aurebesh letters. It was sold at 1.7 credits a cup and 2.7 credits a bowl.
Aurebesh soup is likely a reference to the real-world alphabet soup.
